OL,3,CFormer Labour MP Mike Amesbury has
OL,4,Cprison sentence suspended
OL,6,FHonorary Recorder of Chester Judge
OL,7,FSteven Everett, sitting with two
OL,8,Fmagistrates, imposed another sentence
OL,9,Fof 10 weeks' imprisonment but
OL,10,Fsuspended it for two years.
OL,12,FHe also ordered him to carry out 200
OL,13,Fhours of unpaid work, undertake a 12-
OL,14,Fmonth alcohol monitoring requirement,
OL,15,Fgo on an anger management course and
OL,16,Fcarry out 20 days of rehabilitation
OL,17,Fwork.
OL,19,FAmesbury arrived at court in a prison
OL,20,Fvan and was led into the building in
OL,21,Fhandcuffs by an officer.
