OL,3,CFormer Labour MP Mike Amesbury has
OL,4,Cprison sentence suspended
OL,6,FHis prison sentence leaves the 55-year-
OL,7,Fold politician at risk of being ousted
OL,8,Fif his constituents back a petition
OL,9,Fcalling for a by-election.
OL,11,FAmesbury pleaded guilty in January to
OL,12,Fassaulting Paul Fellows, 45, following
OL,13,Fa row in the street in Frodsham,
OL,14,FCheshire, in the early hours of 26
OL,15,FOctober.
