OL,3,CFormer Labour MP Mike Amesbury has
OL,4,Cprison sentence suspended
OL,6,FThe appeal hearing was told in a
OL,7,Fprepared statement given in a police
OL,8,Finterview, Amesbury initially claimed
OL,9,Fhe had been approached by a man
OL,10,F"shouting and screaming" about local
OL,11,Fand national matters, including a
OL,12,Flocal swing bridge and immigration.
OL,14,FIn the statement, he told police: "I
OL,15,Fthought I was about to be physically
OL,16,Fassaulted by this male. I was
OL,17,Fterrified and felt vulnerable and
OL,18,Fcornered by the male and others in the
OL,19,Fgroup."
