OL,3,CFormer Labour MP Mike Amesbury has
OL,4,Cprison sentence suspended
OL,6,FHe said the man's "arms were swinging"
OL,7,Fand he thought there was no option but
OL,8,Fto "defend" himself.
OL,10,FJudge Everett said: "What he said to
OL,11,Fpolice doesn't seem to fit in with the
OL,12,FCCTV in pretty well any respect."
OL,14,FDaniel Travers, defending, told the
OL,15,Fcourt: "He's now had three nights in
OL,16,Fprison which is an experience he will
OL,17,Fnever forget, certainly."
OL,19,FHe said the "public shaming" and
OL,20,F"embarrassment" had a huge impact on
OL,21,FAmesbury.
