OL,3,CFormer Labour MP Mike Amesbury has
OL,4,Cprison sentence suspended
OL,6,FHe added: "This is a man who will
OL,7,Fcertainly rehabilitate. He will learn
OL,8,Fa very painful lesson."
OL,10,FThe former Labour MP has been sitting
OL,11,Fas an Independent for the Cheshire
OL,12,Fseat since he was suspended by the
OL,13,Fparty after his arrest last year.
OL,15,FThere is no automatic suspension for
OL,16,FMPs serving a custodial sentence,
OL,17,Falthough opposition parties have
OL,18,Fcalled for Amesbury to resign so a by-
OL,19,Felection can be held.
